1. Molim te, *ponesi* ovu knjigu sa sobom. (Please, *take* this book with you.)
2. Želim da *ponesem* sve potrebne stvari na putovanje. (I want to *bring* all the necessary things on the trip.)
3. Da li ćeš *poneti* ovu kutiju na tavan? (Will you *carry* this box to the attic?)
4. Ona će *poneti* kolače za rođendansku proslavu. (She will *bring* the cakes for the birthday party.)
5. Kada *ponosiš* novac u novčaniku, pazi na džepove. (When you *carry* money in your wallet, watch out for your pockets.)
6. *Ponesi* mi novine kada budeš dolazio. ( *Bring* me the newspapers when you come.)
7. Koliko teško je *poneti* sve ove vreće do stana? (How hard is it to *carry* all these bags to the apartment?)
8. Da li si *ponio* kišobran sa sobom? (Did you *take* an umbrella with you?)
9. Ne mogu *poneti* sve ove torbe, pomozi mi. (I can't *carry* all these bags, help me.)
10. Da li ćeš mi *poneti* pismo kada budeš išao na poštu? (Will you *bring* me the letter when you go to the post office?)